Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to feel like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Would you please help me clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you, I have to clean the science room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You had class duty during lunch break,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but you ignored it and left school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, we're locked up inside this school, like birds in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be free sometimes to enjoy{he's saying "fly"} the wide{free} world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that buying croquettes is freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like manual labor,\N could you do some brain work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any more pages left to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.23,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25\fad(0,200)}Left: Class Duty Log\NRight: Roll Book
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You ripped the pages out of the duty journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep throwing those scraps of paper, Tendou will yell at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Scraps of paper? Yui-chan, this is...
