Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing littering the school grounds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you hiding, Kondou Makoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Violating school regulations, skipping cleaning duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and littering the school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, trying to avoid my interrogation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserve capital punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And that means cleaning bathrooms for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he practicing for the scavenger hunt at the autumn sports festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he should be practicing for the folk dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but he has no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, was Tendou's hair always that white?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he dyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's vain about his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, how long do you plan on hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,On the girls' list in this roll book,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,why is number thirteen blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were slacking off on your class duties and didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember right, one girl had to take a leave of absence because of illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't sure when she'd return, \Nso she was taken off the roll book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So they removed this girl's name. That's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we hurry and finish cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall, it was Sugimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto. Oh yes, Sakurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sugimoto Sakurako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was a very cute name. I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.96,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an8}Paper: Prescription for Sugimoto Sakura\NYasohachi Community Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto Sakurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So she used to be my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:13.31,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\b1\bord0\fs34\fnArtificeSSK\c&H875543&\4c&H76524E&\xshad-4\yshad3\pos(344,130)\be1}Episode 4
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.64,0:04:13.31,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(340,400)\b1\bord0\fs40\fnArtificeSSK\c&H875543&\4c&H76524E&\xshad-4\yshad3\be1}Autumn, the Season of Withered Leaves . . .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.20,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1000)\fs25\an8}Sign: Yasohachi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So starting today, I can't go home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Theater Club recruited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a leading role.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:36.64,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25\fad(0,400)}Book: The Last Leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you be happy for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be looking forward to the Cultural Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw it up by getting stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he so uninterested?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sugimoto Sakurako. Sugimoto Sakurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll certainly take photos of Narusawa Yui's triumphant moment on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On a different subject, what's wrong with Sugimoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about Kondou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems interested in that other girl, Sugimoto Sakurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't the wind blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking into this by asking other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She was in class 2-B, but her name was removed from the roll book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The photo on her application form shows that she's a real beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A good cha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, Yui-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're letting that pervert take photos just as he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Saionji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have anything on your mind, you can talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Saionji Aritomo, the hero on stage and your partner as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,will listen to your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. The hero and the heroine appear together for rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We might become the talk of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Narusawa is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-san. Yui-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture of a rejected man chasing a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.47,Overlap,,0,0,0,,A good chance for a photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have to fly away again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it would be easier{quicker} to ask at Reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A paper plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he{she?} cute? He's Turbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nice to meet you. I'm Kondou Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Sugimoto Sakurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you enrolled at Yasohachi Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to go to Yasohachi Academy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I found your name in the roll book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're my classmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I was surprised when I found this in the park over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The paper plane I threw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Accidentally?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, accidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So things do happen accidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasohachi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought my name had been already removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible. We're classmates.{He's lying}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, are you going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to leave school earlier{than usual?} these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have rehearsal in the gymnasium today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having problems with my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you watch me act and give me advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'd rather enjoy it on the day of performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'm a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I forgot that you're ill and was fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a girlfriend, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone beautiful and not sick like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind{having a girlfriend}. Could you still come see me sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not visiting you because I pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I come here every day because I enjoy seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd better recover soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can have a date outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you like your first date to be after you leave here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount Kisaragi Observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That shabby place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I was hospitalized right after I was accepted at Yasohachi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to go there for orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You went there with your classmates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I skipped school that day and went to a movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so I've never been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, that violent teacher, Tendou, made me clean bathrooms for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kondou Makoto, you're going to clean bathrooms for a week!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny. I'd like to hear more about your school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Will tomorrow be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I have checkups throughout visiting hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll come here at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll fall off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All the weak branches have already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So when is lights-out{ time}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be here at ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, ten o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I'm not a suspicious character!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan, is it all right for you to be out of bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm walking... with someone beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kondou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can call me Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like we're lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could die like this{She's justsaying "If I could die..."}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Would you like to go back to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I walked outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine now. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Men are happy to be outdoors, whatever the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Withered leaves are falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When they all fall down, I'm going to wake from my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the nurse. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This...{jacket}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. You can wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll catch a cold on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:15:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'm happy to be outdoors, whatever the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So our member on the Cultural Festival Committee will be Kondou Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:19.02,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs25\move(270,80,-200,35)\fnChalkDustCondensed\bord0\frz-6\c&H9F9463&}Cultural Festival               Committee Election
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not in any club,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's skipped the class's preparations for the Cultural Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cultural Festival Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,does chores like making preliminary arrangements and hanging posters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:34.45,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnChalkDustCondensed\bord0\c&HA9AA77&\pos(65,118)\fscy120}K{\fscy100}ondou
