Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.05,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This is an abuse of democracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer freedom. I don't want to join any club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the success of the Cultural Festival depends on the members of the Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They represent each class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really susceptible to beautiful women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For the week before the Cultural Festival, I couldn't go see Sakurako-chan.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.44,0:16:11.70,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an8}Armband: Cultural Festival Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The bathrooms stink these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did visit her once, late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:35.09,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}Sign: Cultural Festival\NYasohachi Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:54.49,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an8\fad(0,400)}Poster: Cultural Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the Cultural Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited. This year's special event is the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't put you through to a patient unless you're a relative or it's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the Cultural Festival is over, I'll be able to meet her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more she misses me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the fonder her heart will grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-san, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the day of the performance. It makes us nervous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A Cultural Festival Committee member and an astonishing photographer.
