Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You two seem to be getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll keep that up and support us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,as the highlight of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Yui-san, let's go rehearse.
