Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He said I'm an astonishing photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people {\i1}do{\i0\fscx150} {\r}recognize my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm strongly opposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to all forms of violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiki-kun, will you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I recognize your skills as a photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
