Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou-kun, you've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a good idea to take photos as a record of the festival.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.34,0:18:37.59,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(200,324)\bord0.1\fs25\frz-4\c&HD7C7D5&\3c&HD7C7D5&\fnChinacat\be1}Cotton Candy
