Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as a member of the committee, that comes naturally to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I hope you two enjoy it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get some compensation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If you print all of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about a footbridge\N where you can take panty shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better keep your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cultural Festival, the biggest event at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I tell her the story of how I directed it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan will look on me with passionate eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The play with Narusawa Yui-san in the leading role is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Why is Yui playing against that bastard Aritomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:15.28,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}Armband: Cultural Festival Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She visited his villa in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I wonder if there's a love scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I should at least check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I been drawing until today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,His acting is really miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have left of my life is that one leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that one leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When that leaf falls, I will die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is wavering. My life is fluttering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind is getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, spare that last leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Withered leaves are falling.{14:07}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Withered leaves are falling.{14:07}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When they all fall down...{14:12}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:45.22,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(434,320)\bord0\c&H504244&\fnArial}Visiting\N hours\N are\N over
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.60,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,321.5)\bord0\c&H504244&\fnArial}Visiting\N hours\N are\N over
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.31,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(40,0)\fs25\an8}Sign: Yasohachi Community Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Sakurako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dying... That was sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,After such good care for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be sad around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan... is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan... is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:29.18,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25\fad(400,400)}Sign: Yasohachi Academy Cultural Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I cried watching this year's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The heroine was a really good actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She really appeared to be in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-san. Leave that guy alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate the success of our play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? What's wrong, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Yui-san? There's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That applause was to celebrate us as the hero and heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's take advantage of these circumstances and join the folk dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go over to the folk dance first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but can I borrow your bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount Kisaragi Observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's quite far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. We don't have school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura... ko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive. She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.91,0:23:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was your bird that died.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of putting Turbo's soul on a paper plane and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.46,0:23:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you made a paper plane as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a memory with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be in bed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.58,0:24:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.73,0:24:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.89,0:24:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.20,0:24:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.80,0:24:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,look.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.70,0:24:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.64,0:24:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.22,0:24:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.82,0:25:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.11,0:25:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful, Sakurako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.11,0:25:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Makoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.60,0:25:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.33,0:25:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.20,0:26:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.55,0:26:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't usually come to the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.41,0:26:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly. I'm a regular patron here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.40,0:26:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical strength isn't enough for men.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.53,0:26:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We also need to be good at studying and the martial arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.27,0:26:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You kinda sound like Tendou. He must be influencing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.93,0:26:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Tendou influence me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.45,0:26:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.33,0:26:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you bringing these into the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to exchange them with Shimizu in the library...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.08,0:26:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.38,0:26:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.07,0:26:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou Makoto-senpai, please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.11,0:26:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.00,0:26:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.58,0:26:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsuzuki Kozue from class 1-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.62,0:26:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you. Will you be my boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.34,0:26:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
