Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.51,0:27:48.56,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}People in the street looked at me strangely
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.52,0:27:58.65,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}mada haru asai san gatsu no gogo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.65,0:28:02.95,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}tsumetai ame no sora miage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.52,0:27:58.65,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}On an early spring afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.65,0:28:02.95,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I looked up at the sky in the cold rain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.95,0:28:10.00,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}odoritaku naru youna kibun de aruita
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.95,0:28:10.00,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I walked with an urge to dance
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.92,0:28:24.51,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}arifureta nichijyou ni itsuka kokoro ga kumotte ta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.92,0:28:24.51,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}My heart was clouded by the familiar days
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.51,0:28:32.06,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}sonna koto sae kizukazu ni ita
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.51,0:28:32.06,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I didn't understand anything
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.02,0:28:36.02,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.02,0:28:36.02,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.36,0:28:46.37,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}honno sasayakana nandemo nai youna yuuki dakeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.36,0:28:46.37,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}It was a small piece of courage, almost like nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.37,0:28:53.58,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}sonna koto de naze ka sukoshi kokoro ga hareta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.37,0:28:53.58,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I don't know why, but it brightened my heart a bit
